**Description:** This rule defines how the public LIA listings page functions, including layout, filter options, data structure, and visibility behavior.

```
# LIA Post Listing Rules

## URL
- `/lia-plats`

## Functionality
- Publicly accessible list of all published LIA offers.
- Users can filter by:
  - Category
  - City
  - Company name
  - Keyword search (title or description)

## Display
- Uses a card grid layout (`<LiaPostCard>`).
- Each card includes: title, category, city, short description, and link to detail page.
- Pagination or infinite scroll (TBD).

## Security
- Only published listings are shown.
```